urned during the battle.  The Seventh Hammer poisoned me, struck me and finally sent a lightning bolt of blackness into my heart.  All the while, Ravnanger tried to summon the powers of The Tribunal.  <br><br>I was able to fight off The Seventh Hammer but was greatly weakened.  Between the arms of my brothers, I was carried back to the Halas ramp.  The Seventh Hammer and Ethroth were gone... but I felt in my heart that The Seventh Hammer would be back.  Next time, we would need more MacLears to bring forth the power of The Tribunal. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmaclearfrm6.showPrevMessage?topicID=67.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmaclearfrm6.showNextMessage?topicID=67.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmaclearfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=67.topic&index=4><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmaclearfrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=67.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmaclearfrm6.threadControl?topicID=67.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmaclearfrm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=67.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmaclearfrm6.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=67.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></t